The following rather extreme claim on memory causes a
segmentation fault on my installation:

fred <- matrix(1:1200, 20, 60)

littleOP <- function(x, y)
{
  z <- as.vector(x) %*% t(as.vector(y))
  dim(z) <- c(dim(x), dim(y))
